title: The Stanley Parable [FINAL] 2013 (PC) - Foxy Games

Details
**********

Released: 2013
Name: The Stanley Parable 
Platform: PC 
Publication Type: Pirates 
Genre: Adventure , Indie 
Developer: Galactic Cafe 
Language: English, Russian, Italian, Spanish, Danish, Dutch 
Language voice: English 



Description
***************

The Stanley Parable a game in which you will play for Stanley and will not play 
for the Stanley. You will go through the story, and you will not go through the story. You will have a choice. The game will end, and the game will never end. Controversy controversy, violated rules of the games, and then broken again. 
This world is not for you to understand.


System Requirements
************************

OS: Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8
Processor: 3.0 GHz P4, Dual Core 2.0 (or higher) or AMD64X2 (or higher)
RAM: 2 GB RAM
Video: Video card must be 128 MB or more and should be a DirectX 9-compatible with support for Pixel Shader 2.0 (ATI Radeon X800 or higher / NVIDIA GeForce 7600 or higher / Intel HD Graphics 2000 or higher).
Hard Drive: 3 GB available space
Sound: DirectX 9.0c compatible


Instructions
**************

Install and Play!
Keep Seeding!
Have Fun!
